      <p class="text-sm text-base-content/70 mt-3">Self-hosted. No license. Fully functional.</p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm flex-grow">
        <li>✓ All 31 detectors + session vectors</li>
        <li>✓ SQLite persistence (zero ops)</li>
        <li>✓ Local dashboard, static YAML config</li>
        <li>✓ ASP.NET Core Identity (local accounts)</li>
        <li>✓ Local Ollama LLM escalation</li>
        <li class="text-base-content/40">– No central control plane</li>
        <li class="text-base-content/40">– No fleet dashboard</li>
