      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm flex-grow">
        <li>✓ Everything in OSS</li>
        <li>✓ Postgres + Redis persistence</li>
        <li>✓ Control plane + live config editor</li>
        <li>✓ 3 gateway instances, 3 portal users</li>
